<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="poemXX">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>viyaṉpulam paṭarnta pallā neṭuvēṟu</l>
<l>maṭalai māṇiḻa lacaiviṭak kōvalar</l>
<l>vītatai mullaip pūppaṟik kuntu</l>
<l>kuṟuṅkō leṟinta neṭuñcevik kuṟumuya</l>
<l>ṉeṭunīrp parappiṉ vāḷaiyo ṭukaḷuntu</l>
<l>toṭalai yalkuṟ ṟoṭittōṇ makaḷir</l>
<l>kaṭalāṭik kayampāyntu</l>
<l>kaḻineytaṟ pūkkuṟūuntu</l>
<l>paintaḻai tuyalvaruñ ceṟuviṟ ṟa........</l>
<l>....................................latti</l>
<l>vaḷara vēṇṭu mavaḷē yeṉṟu</l>
<l>mārama ruḻappatu mamariya ḷāki</l>
<l>muṟañcevi yāṉai vēntar</l>
<l>maṟaṅkeḻu neñcaṅ koṇṭoḷit tōḷē.</l>
</lg>
